      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·生民之什·007.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">泂酌.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>泂酌彼行潦，挹彼注茲，可以餴饎。豈弟君子，民之父母。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Take the pool-water from a distance;
Draw it into one vessel and let it flow to another,
And it may be used to stream rice or millet.
How much more should the happy and courteous sovereign,
Be the parent of the people!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
